values: I just thought I'd do a quick update to say that I haven't cut in ages. I think the last was my hand.. But I do remember having cut my arm a great deal... But I think that was before my hand.. I'm not good with time, so it's all confused. I did cut my hair with a razor though, it looks pretty good. My counsellor reckoned that I should be a hairdresser haha. Everyone thinks that I'm doing better and my psychiatrist doesn't mind being proven wrong about the drugs, just as long as I'm doing good.. Maybe I don't have what he thinks I have. Who really knows. Anyways, I have to go, I'll be back hopefully tomorrow to comment on everyone. Till then, have fun.

Hey, this entry is for I haven't been around to say this, but...

HAPPY BIRTHDAY FOR THE 4TH!

I hope everything was great fun! Sorry it's late, I just haven't been on.
Sometimes, I just wish I could cry. I don't know how to. I can't. I just wish I could sometimes. I feel the need to cry, but I can't, I don't like it.

life is good, life is great,
as long as you take time to sedate,
life is good life is great,
don't forget to masturbate.

hahaha. I just remembered that. My ex wrote it for me a while ago to make me laugh. It worked too. I was thinking "Life is sweet, Life is great" and that came into my head. hahaha, yeah, I feel good!

I just can't cope anymore. I fuck up over and over. I can never win! Fucking life. Maybe I shouldn't tell people about things, they just can't deal with it. It hurts them to know what I do to myself. I don't know what it's feels like for them to see me like this or anything. I hate it. That's it, I'm not going to say anything to them anymore. I'll only be selective about what I say. I'll be "fake" again. That way they can't be upset. I'll be what they want me to be, and I'll do what they want me to do. I'm not going to be me anymore. I'll say good bye to myself now, we may never see each other again... But I am going to go to counselling, so maybe I will see myself there. That will be my grave.
I just need someone to talk to, someone that understands me. Is there anyone out there???

Just my first journal entry....

I thought I'd say FUCK!
